name: MEC Travel Light Packing Cube 3-Pack
description: It’s hip to be square. Keep the contents of your luggage organized and wrinkle-free with lightweight packing cubes. They also useful for keeping shoes and dirty laundry separate from the clean stuff.Made of nylon with a water-resistant silicone coating.Semi-transparent top material aids identification of contents.Large clamshell lid with dual zipper pulls for easy access.Webbing handle for carrying or hanging.Sold as a package of three cubes in three different colours so you can colour-code your life.
